Now I'm asking that you

00:13.700 --> 00:21.732
say something so this will record. Let's pick you 
up over there. Okay. What do you want to talk about?

00:28.903 --> 00:30.906
I wish we could talk about what a nice week it's 
been. Well, I want an idea.

00:38.296 --> 00:41.361
Now let's see if it's doing any better in between 
us. Let's see. Give your name, rate, horsepower,

