the freshman saw, well, they spoke to everyone, 
but if the freshman saw an upperclassman of his

22:03.107 --> 22:21.613
outfit, he spoke to Mr. So-and-so, and if Mr. 
So-and-so was talking to somebody else, The

22:22.201 --> 22:32.133
freshman either knew the other person's name and 
